text: "Starting Over" is a 1980 song by country singer Tammy Wynette and is the second single from her 21st studio album Only Lonely Sometimes. It went to number 17 on the Billboard Hot Country Singles charts and number 41 on the Canadian Country Singles charts. ==Track listings== ;7" vinyl single * "Starting Over" – 3:07 * "I'll Be Thinking of You" – 3:58 == References == Category:1980 songs Category:Country songs Category:Tammy Wynette songs
